cscie97.asn1.knowledge.engine

Class KnowledgeGraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • cscie97.asn1.knowledge.engine.KnowledgeGraph

  • public class KnowledgeGraph
extends java.lang.Object
    KnowledgeGraph manages the set of active Triples.KnowledgeGraph is a singleton, meaning there is only one instance of this class.
    Author:
    APGalush
